Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡,为了打倒支配着遥远星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又再一次成为救世主,进行冒险旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在超力布村的星之风宫殿里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把第一星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露易·玛格西打倒了的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令星之风吹起,令第一星界再次变为四处开满花的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,跟着是第二星界了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七话\N沙海的海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到第二星界了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连嘴巴内也满是沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会这样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是沙漠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,大叔,在哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我吗?法鲁战王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃伊啊…真不清洁的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个满是灰尘的房间是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再打自己身体,把灰尘弄出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了,我的第二星界大沙漠化计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的地区做得最好呢,多坏达大人也非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多谢你,我最喜欢的就是沙尘滚滚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管说多少次 我对这身体的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是对于有尘埃飞出来令我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫了你不要弄灰尘出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起,不自觉地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗?木乃伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实那个渡把第一星界恢复了原状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已侵入了我们的第二星界了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果渡在你地区出现,就立刻消灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把他们变成大沙漠上的沙尘给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪糕…刨冰…可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啤酒…日本酒…威士忌开水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁…西瓜…芥子明太子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树叶…荞头…羊羹!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用"n"音结尾就玩完了 (在玩接词)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么炎热之中竟还在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子真有精力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师傅,你好重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有蜃楼海市了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,不是蜃楼海市,是海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,这次也许会是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是海市蜃楼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌海市蜃楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有这么多水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么海市蜃楼,全部消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在这里弄个水潭出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,为什么我会遇上这些事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哗!太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对这么重要的水干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要替河马洗身,立刻上来!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河…河马?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河马,河马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个泉水是这附近最后的泉水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来之前,这里还是一片翠绿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在,却变成了这样的沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然会变成了沙漠的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条村从以前起就有种叫沙蚯蚓的生物在这里住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙蚯蚓帮助我们令土地松软起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来和村民们是很融洽相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多坏达的手下把它变成了可怕的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这附近全变成沙漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是多坏达弄出来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙蚯蚓出现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要大意,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,不要大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师傅也是,想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡 对了,用星之西班牙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之西班牙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星之西班牙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以自由地控制动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那些雪糕给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙蚯蚓,听我的说话做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?渡,不是没有响吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙走了进去,打不响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,劲辣七味粉之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了把盖打开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子第一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙蚯蚓,你不再做坏事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再和村民们和好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?师傅,那支叉怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑者!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多坏达的手下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字也有火和子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说太浪费了,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说无条件给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这叉交换怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这星龙剑是圣龙妃大人给我的重要的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会和那支便宜叉交换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这样吧,我们来比谁跑得快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我胜了那剑就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,还不快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是男人与男人间的决斗啊,你不接受吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人的话就来决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是任意胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵捉贼…来捉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?好像到了什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算…算了,省了出去找他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终点,万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我胜了,剑是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是同时到达吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对,我绝对比你快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?要打吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂,不可以打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我先到所以是我胜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?这是男人和男人的胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和女人的你没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子第一,火美子了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得…得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真顽强呢,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第二星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁战王的部下木乃伊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多坏达的一党呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰尘攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很蒙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?这绷带攻击,会把你们勒至死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转陀螺,转陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!是草莓内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶,看见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷卷…这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沙上他比较快,小心点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的迟钝龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机会了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙雷拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那牙内是藏着不论什么魔神也能打倒的剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当毒蔓延至全身时就是你的死期了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是火美子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是时候收拾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起中毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,操蛇之术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!停手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点用解毒剂的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,那条蛇的牙内有解毒剂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼在旋转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠你们,沙蚯蚓恢复原本的温驯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不算什么,小事一件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对会令第二星界恢复一片翠绿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我从木乃伊那处拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看看这处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是星界文字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼中的砂砾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要令沙漠恢复翠绿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把星石放到基拿基拿山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会读星界文字吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是胡说吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信的话不信也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑我一定会拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来玩兵捉贼吧,山火子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫海火子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵!山火子,呀呵!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之已知道了令这第二星界恢复原状的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我们要好好加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

